<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zitteliana.97.115682.figure10>
    dc:description "Figure 10. Pyrgulinae (Hydrobiidae) of the Kolankaya I fauna. A-E. Prososthenia cf. Prososthenia sturanyi Prososthenia communis Willmann, 1981, RGM 962615, sample 2. F-J. P. cf. Prososthenia sturanyi Prososthenia communis, SNSB-BSPG 2023 XII 11, sample 2. K-Q. Xestopyrguloides? sagitta sp. nov., holotype, RGM 962616, sample 2. R. Xestopyrguloides? heldreichii (Fuchs, 1870), lectotype (designated by Willmann 1981), NHMW 1878 XX 28, Megara, Pliocene. S-U. Xestopyrguloides? sp., RGM 1365347, sample 2. Scale bars: 1 mm (A-D, F-I, K-N, R-T); 100 μm (E, J, O-Q)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/950747" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

